title: Savory Trumps Sweet In This Bourbon Glazed Pork Pot Pie With Bacon Latticed  Crust — Snack Break
description:
For the people who forgo holiday dessert spreads in favor of another helping of meat, this pie is for you. From Butcher Bar in Queens, New York, comes a barbecue-studded pot pie complete with bacon lattice and bourbon glaze.
